features: What You Will Get: the package contains 16 pieces of baby bottle labels in 4 different colors (green, yellow, gray and blue), 4 pieces per color, and 1 piece of dry erase marker, sufficient quantity to meet your needs and replacements

Quality and Reliable Material: the labels for daycare are made of quality silicone material, which is smooth and reliable to use, not easy to fade or break, writable and erasable, safe and long lasting

Elastic and Reusable: the daycare bottle labels are elastic, just stretch out them and wrap them around the baby bottle; And the labels for bottles are washable and reusable, the marks can be removed by washing with warm water, high temperature resistant, and dishwasher safe

Proper Size: the diameter of the reusable bottle labels is approx. 6.4 cm/ 2.5 inches and the width is approx. 1.5 cm/ 0.6 inches, which is suitable for most baby bottles, reducing the area that blocks the water level of the bottle

Easy to Distinguish: the bottle labels daycare reusable with different colors allow you to distinguish easily, you can accurately label the bottle with your baby's name, date, and feeding instructions, to make sure the baby is healthy and well fed
